# Public Repository

This repo is PUBLIC. NEVER add secrets, tokens, credentials, personal data, private keys, or internal hostnames. Use runtime env vars for secrets.

# Maintain Agent Docs

When you change the repo, update `AGENTS.md` and any affected `.cursor/skills/*/SKILL.md` or `.cursor/rules/` to stay in sync. Outdated agent docs are worse than none.
